					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Great article! The exploration of 4D mechanics was engaging and walked the line between well-grounded and not being too esoteric nicely.</p> <p>In particular,</p> <blockquote> <p>One agent is unaccounted for — the coordinate position of their body within the anomaly is unknown.</p> </blockquote> <p>did a lot in demonstrating the complexity of the space with very few words.</p> <p>Bravo. +1</p> 
				 	]]>
